info.name: Cant Desk
info.description: We know that when space is limited—think city apartment or a college dorm room—your desk can’t be the focal point of your room. We also know it should still look good; after all, it’s the stage for your next masterpiece! The cantilevered shape of Blu Dot’s Cant Desk helps it blend in, even as its combination of warm walnut and bright orange steel accents cuts a chic silhouette.
